0.name: Inspiron™ 14 7000 Series
0.descp: You asked for greater mobility and we delivered a whole new experience. With a forged aluminum design and impressively thin profile, it’s trimmer yet stronger. Add in long battery life, more power, and an ultra-bright Full HD touch screen (optional), and it’s the ultimate on-the-go taskmaster. Your wish is our design.

1.name: Inspiron™ 15 7000 Series
1.descp: You asked for greater multimedia power on-the-go and our team delivered a knockout. Accelerated graphics. Richer audio. An ultra-bright Full HD touch screen (optional). It’s thinner, stronger and brighter so you can enjoy more of what you love. Anywhere you go. Your wish is our design.

2.name: Inspiron™ 11 3000 Series
2.descp:
It’s only 11.6". But don’t let the size of the Inspiron 11 fool you. Its long-lasting battery, spacious edge-to-edge touch screen and roomy hard drive
keep you connected, productive and fully entertained everywhere you go.

3.name: XPS™ 12 Convertible UltraBook™
3.descp: With tap-to-pair and tap-to-share features, and designed to be even faster, the XPS™ 12 Convertible Ultrabook™ is now a better laptop and tablet in one.

4.name: XPS™ 13
4.descp: Enjoy the view from almost any angle with the new Dell™ XPS™ 13 Ultrabook™. Now with an optional full HD screen.

5.name: Inspiron™ 23 AIO Desktop
5.descp: Is it the cutting-edge 4th Generation Intel® Core™ processors, Windows 8 and generous storage? Or is it the ultra-slim design and Full HD 1080p touch screen? The true power of the Inspiron 23 All-in-One is the way it brings excitement and productivity to everyone in your home.

6.name: Latitude™ 10  Tablet
6.descp: Latitude™ 10 is the tablet that’s built for business with easy management and security, and a swappable battery for go-anywhere productivity.

7.name: Vostro™ 5470
7.descp: Work smarter and look sharp with the new Vostro 5470 14-inch Windows® 8 laptop.  With faster performance, touch screen option1, and the essential security and support you need to keep you on the winning path.

8.name: Inspiron™ 14
8.descp: Introducing the affordable new Inspiron™ 14. Featuring a touch screen that takes full advantage of Windows 8. Thin and light, and with an impressive battery life, this laptop keeps up with you on your busiest days.

9.name: Inspiron™ 14R
9.descp: The Inspiron™ 14R. Now featuring a touch screen to take full advantage of Windows 8, this slim laptop keeps up with your busy schedule at work or at play.

10.name: Inspiron™ 15
10.descp: The Inspiron 15 now features a beautiful touch screen. Affordable, portable and featuring impressive battery life, it’s the Windows 8-powered laptop you’ll take virtually anywhere.battery life, this laptop keeps up with you on your busiest days.

11.name: Inspiron™ 15R
11.descp: The chic Inspiron™ 15R, now features a touch screen to take full advantage of Windows 8. With a beautiful brushed aluminum finish, built-in DVD and optional colors, it will entertain you virtually anywhere.

12.name: XPS™ 11
12.descp:
TThe new XPS 11 2-in-1 Ultrabook™ takes performance and design to the next level. Premium materials, such as carbon fiber and damage resistant Corning® Gorilla® Glass NBT™, maximize durability. The UltraSharp™ Quad HD display delivers stunning detail, and the solid surface
backlit touch keyboard is designed to withstand tablet usage.

13.name: XPS™ 15
13.descp: Dell celebrates the passion to create with the Dell XPS 15. A high-performance laptop with 4th gen Intel® Core ™ processors, Windows 8 Pro, a 15.6” optional UltraSharp™ QHD   touch display constructed of damage-resistant Corning® Gorilla® Glass NBTTM. We can’t wait to see what you do with it.
